design document:

http://docs.google.com/View?id=ajd93zkqrjq5_342cqdrxqcd

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Prerequisites
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

In Ubuntu 9.04 (Karmic), python-facebook is too old.
please install python-facebook 0.svn20090724-1.1 from lucid.

http://packages.ubuntu.com/lucid/all/python-facebook/download

In Debian Squeeze/Sid please install python-facebook:
# apt-get install python-facebook

In Arch Linux please install pyfacebook-git from AUR.
$ yaourt -S pyfacebook-git

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Configuration
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

you need get secert.py and put it in wallbox/wallbox/, please contact 
yurenju (AT) gmail (DOT) com. currently, we can't run application without 
secery key.

if you know how to run application without secert key, please 
fork and patch it.


-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Run
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

$ cd wallbox/wallbox
$ python ./__init__.py

Open another terminal
$ cd wallbox/data
$ ./wizard.py

please "login" and press "continue"
after that, plase press ctrl + C to finish Wizard.

$ ./notification.py (initial receive data)
$ ./wallbox.py


